{"tid":2136112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中醫考試拒延期 數百人擬罷考","createTime":"2020-08-02T01:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T03:46:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e038f0506839ff6f8f5a25dd00aa985342698a","tid":2136112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/DIV2LV762DUITHZEUIESXEQZVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FDIV2LV762DUITHZEUIESXEQZVE%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=09a16a09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FDIV2LV762DUITHZEUIESXEQZVE%2F&h=9041b7bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/DIV2LV762DUITHZEUIESXEQZVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中醫考試拒延期 數百人擬罷考<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ks4pxNx31gxRy2thEyaLMI19mCo=/813x513/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AL6R2RRMFPUEFNVKXYQXPDGZCM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fks4pxNx31gxRy2thEyaLMI19mCo%3D%2F813x513%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAL6R2RRMFPUEFNVKXYQXPDGZCM.gif&h=58b657d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n考生早前收到准考證，須赴新蒲崗考評局面試（紅框示）。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，周一（3日）開考的中醫執業資格試面試部份如期舉行，有考生指考評局試場在新蒲崗「重災區」，擔心赴考染疫，中醫委員會（中委會）卻拒絕網上考試或延期，數百名考生不排除罷考。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：亞博啟用收30患者 走廊漏水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙區舉行 考生憂心<br />\n<br />\n讀者陳小姐（50歲）報考了今年度的中醫執業資格試，筆試已於6月完成，面試則定於本月3日至17日分批進行。陳小姐說，考生要到新蒲崗的考評局應考，屆時會有兩至三位考官及一位職員在場，考試時間50分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n「喺新蒲崗呀！黃大仙區幾多確診個案先得㗎！」陳小姐說，過去兩星期疫情越趨嚴峻，眼見其他考試，特別是西醫執業試也。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，上周四（30日），太平道2號太平花園一名37歲女。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，女患者當時偕男友人離開大廈，。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"bd4612324f5023fa91255f01c9c3f743ff89fbb7","tid":2136112,"uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"新蒲崗同黃大仙同慈雲山都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e0f3942931d1460b48273b1ec13f6f082cc687","tid":2136112,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:42:35.000Z","msg":"唔好考"},{"pid":"7b25f17a071441d40992e3c4c519df5291a45b00","tid":2136112,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"其實其他考試有冇延期"},{"pid":"50d1eab402f0c9e1574d2cdc6cf28f614aa0c89a","tid":2136112,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩 即場把個脈咪就有無事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}